  "detailed_description": "<strong>※Note※ A controller with two analog sticks is required to play.</strong><br><br>\"LIBLADE\" is a side-scrolling action game that features slashing action utilizing the analog stick.<br>Use the analog stick to quickly unleash a powerful slash that will cover the screen.<br><br><strong>Flick the stick, and come on, slash!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/a25f2e4eea4fe49e8551c4e88b6fffb8.poster.avif?t=1672243062\" width=384 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/a25f2e4eea4fe49e8551c4e88b6fffb8.webm?t=1672243062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/a25f2e4eea4fe49e8551c4e88b6fffb8.mp4?t=1672243062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Rotate the stick to carve up your enemies!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/4734988e1f0d8ea46ae58a43bd091c83.poster.avif?t=1672243062\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/4734988e1f0d8ea46ae58a43bd091c83.webm?t=1672243062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/4734988e1f0d8ea46ae58a43bd091c83.mp4?t=1672243062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong> Time it just right to reflect enemy attacks!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/925e74ef0bbc100fea9bcda9419bf7fb.poster.avif?t=1672243062\" width=354 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/925e74ef0bbc100fea9bcda9419bf7fb.webm?t=1672243062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/925e74ef0bbc100fea9bcda9419bf7fb.mp4?t=1672243062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the area and defeat many enemies to grow your skill tree and learn new techniques.<br>\"LIBLADE\" is a pure action game.<br>Gain new abilities and defeat your enemies with a variety of slashes to reach the end of the line.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/9791d2ecda8ce0031991be8c11c2ae4b.poster.avif?t=1672243062\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/9791d2ecda8ce0031991be8c11c2ae4b.webm?t=1672243062\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736300/extras/9791d2ecda8ce0031991be8c11c2ae4b.mp4?t=1672243062\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Come and experience the new twin-stick slash action.<br><strong> Feel the joy of Stick-mashing!!!</strong><br><br>Initial play time: approx. 3.5-6.5 hours (from test player)",
